These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, writing
3 different games are played: billiard, domino, whist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, september, november
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, turtle
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, balloon-flower, zinnia
House: futuristic, townhouse, modern
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person playing whist##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person playing domino##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 5. the futuristic house is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking tea##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | lemonade   | tea      |
| Hobby          | writing      | skydiving     | reading     |
| Game           | domino | whist  | billiard   |
| Birthday   | september   | november     | august  |
| Pet   | goldfish      | rabbit      | turtle      |
| Flower   | zinnia      | balloon-flower    | daffodil   |
| House         | futuristic    | townhouse | modern |

