.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
House: palace, victorian, farmhouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, november
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, western
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, eggplant, raspberry
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, trance, blues
3 different games are played: whist, chess, mah-jongg
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 2. the farmhouse house is the fan of funk##1
 3. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
 4. the victorian house is the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
 8. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating nectarine##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| House         | victorian | farmhouse  | palace     |
| Birthday           | april        | december | november    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | western    | mystery    |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | hot-chocolate    | iced-tea   |
| Food           | raspberry        | eggplant    | nectarine        |
| Music-Genre         | trance     | funk  | blues     |
| Game     | mah-jongg         | chess       | whist |

