The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, water-polo, basketball
House: modern, cape-cod, victorian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, superhero
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daffodil, zinnia
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, writing, board-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, classical, trance
 1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is the person who likes brown##1
 7. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
10. the victorian house is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Color      | brown   | mauve         | yellow |
| Sport          | basketball  | water-polo        | surfing    |
| House           | modern | cape-cod  | victorian  |
