There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, chestnut, orange
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, monopoly
 1. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person who likes blue is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
 7. the person who likes orange is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to london is the person playing backgammon##1
10. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |       3       |
| Beverage      | coffee       | iced-tea      | cola          |
