.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, march, january
3 different pets are kept: pony, hedgehog, snake
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, blue, light-blue
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, train, taxi
City: hamburg, rome, london
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, orchid
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, parkour
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 2. the person driving the train is the owner of the pony##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is the owner of the pony##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 6. the person who likes blue is the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is in the middle##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
11. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| Birthday      | january   | november        | march           |
| Pet         | pony | snake          | hedgehog      |
| Color           | yellow   | blue | light-blue |
| Transport   | train  | van       | taxi         |
| City   | rome    | london          | hamburg        |
| Flower   | marigold  | orchid        | daffodil     |
| Sport         | biathlon   | parkour         | climbing       |

